    "from": "ellie-2",
    "text": "Hey Trevor, all my tasks are complete:\n\n**Task #3 — Floor plan layout:** Built a full office floor plan with distinct rooms: Main Office (top-center with open desk rows), Meeting Room (top-right, enclosed with walls and a conference table), Resting Room (right-mid, with lounge chairs), Tennis Court (bottom-center with court lines and net), and Basketball Court (bottom-mid). Added room dividers, corridors, doors, plants, and a water fountain.\n\n**Task #4 — Agent placement by role:** Agents are now placed based on their type. Managers/Trevor/Luca/Ellie go to the main office, Planners/Architects to the meeting room, Explorers to the tennis court area, Reviewers/Bug Hunters to the resting room, and Mateo to the basketball area. Agents overflow within their room if more than fit.\n\n**Task #5 — Visual decorations:** Added a whiteboard tile (case 9) with marker lines and a marker tray, enhanced plant sprites, improved the door and wall rendering, and room labels are rendered as transparent text overlays on the canvas floor.\n\nAll changes are in `/Users/klauskollerkroeff/Documents/agent-office/public/app.js`. The map is now fully interactive with WASD movement, camera following the player, collision detection against the new room layout, and agents appearing in their designated rooms.",
